---
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<section
  class="relative flex min-h-screen flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden bg-ivory"
  aria-labelledby="hero-heading"
>
  <!-- Background video.  Absolutely positioned to fill the section.
       Note: prefers-reduced-motion is NOT honored here on purpose — the
       video is the lab's signature visual and the wash keeps it gentle. -->
  <video
    class="absolute top-0 left-0 z-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
    autoplay
    muted
    loop
    playsinline
    preload="auto"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <source src="/video/hero.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
  </video>

  <!-- Ivory wash to lift the headline off the video.  Strongest at the top
       where the headline sits, then transparent through the middle so the
       video remains visible, then a soft pad at the bottom for the footer
       caption. -->
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-[1] bg-gradient-to-b from-ivory/70 via-transparent to-ivory/50"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- Foreground content.  z-10 keeps it above the video and wash. -->
  <div
    class="relative z-10 mx-auto flex w-full max-w-content flex-1 flex-col justify-start page-x"
    style="padding-top: 22vh;"
  >
    <p class="eyebrow reveal" style="text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(250,250,247,0.85);">
      {site.name}
    </p>

    <h1
      id="hero-heading"
      class="reveal mt-6 font-display font-semibold tracking-tight text-charcoal"
      style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem); line-height: 1.12; text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(250,250,247,0.7), 0 0 28px rgba(250,250,247,0.9);"
    >
      <span class="block">AI時代に、</span>
      <span class="block">感情でゆとりをつくる。</span>
    </h1>

    <div
      class="reveal mt-10 max-w-prose font-display font-medium text-charcoal"
      style="font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.5vw, 1.5rem); line-height: 1.7; text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(250,250,247,0.65), 0 0 20px rgba(250,250,247,0.75);"
    >
      <p>感情をはかり、社会に返す。</p>
      <p>誰もが、すこし息のしやすい時代へ。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
      <a href="/affectosphere/" class="btn-solid">
        Affectosphereとは
        <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/research/" class="btn-ghost">
        研究テーマ
        <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pb-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</section>
